:: motherKissPBedroom [incest romantic]
/* Mother - Bedroom Kiss */

<<set $location = "Parents Room">>
<<advanceTime 10>>

<<narrative>>
The bedroom is quiet, peaceful. Your mother is in her nightgown, getting ready for bed. She turns as you enter, a soft smile on her lips.
<</narrative>>

<<dialog "mother">>
"Coming to say goodnight?"
<</dialog>>

<<dialog "player">>
"Something like that..."
<</dialog>>

<<narrative>>
You step closer to her. The air between you feels charged, electric. She doesn't move away.
<</narrative>>

<<dialog "mother">>
<<if $characters.mother.stats.love < 80>>
//Her breath catches slightly as you lean in.//

"Sweetie... what are you..."

//But she doesn't pull away as you press a gentle kiss to her cheek, lingering just a moment too long.//
<<else>>
//Her eyes flutter closed as you cup her face gently.//

"We shouldn't..."

//But even as she says it, she tilts her head up, and your lips meet in a soft, tender kiss.//
<</if>>
<</dialog>>

<<set $characters.mother.stats.love += 8>>
<<set $characters.mother.stats.lust += 5>>
<<if $characters.mother.stats.love > 100>><<set $characters.mother.stats.love = 100>><</if>>
<<if $characters.mother.stats.lust > 100>><<set $characters.mother.stats.lust = 100>><</if>>

<div class="stat-change">
    <span class="icon icon-heart icon-14"></span> Love +8
    <span class="icon icon-arousal icon-14"></span> Lust +5
</div>

<<btn "Continue" "CharacterInteraction">>
